      audio: '<strong>Audio feedback:</strong> Surprisingly efficient — spoken feedback often takes less time than writing and can be warmer and more nuanced. Recording 2–3 minute voice notes per assignment is a practical strategy.',
      targeted: '<strong>Focus on key areas:</strong> Very practical. Identify 1–2 high-priority improvements per assignment rather than annotating every error. Focused feedback is more actionable and manageable to produce.',
